* More accurate answers
* Uses latest or private data
* Cost-efficient (no need to retrain model)
7. Disadvantages
* Slightly slower (extra retrieval step)
* Needs proper chunking and embeddings
* Requires setup (DB + pipeline)
8. Tools used in RAG
* LangChain
* LlamaIndex
* OpenAI / Gemini models
* Vector DBs (FAISS, Pinecone, Weaviate)
9. Simple Formula
RAG = Retrieval + Generation
